prop.text: Ancient scriptures are preserved here at the temple
These tablets mentions the return of the darkness
It is our duty to seek those who have the power to change our worlds coming destiny
"And from emptiness, the land started to rise..."
"...Life began, and light began to prosper..."
"...But as shine scorches the earth, the shadows returns in greater strength."
The spirit must be able to conquer the minds fear
Reach the end and you may be the one we are looking for
